---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service — Tam"
  description="Terms of service for tam.buzz and Tam Philosophical Counseling."
>
  <main>
    <nav
      class="fixed top-0 w-full z-50 border-b"
      style="background: rgba(17, 24, 39, 0.7); backdrop-filter: blur(20px); border-color: rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.1);"
    >
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-4">
        <a
          href="/#cta"
          class="text-amber-400 hover:text-amber-300 no-underline text-lg font-medium transition-colors"
        >
          ← tam.buzz
        </a>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="py-20 pt-28 px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Terms of Service</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-500 mb-12">Effective date: March 20, 2026</p>

        <div
          class="prose prose-lg prose-invert prose-a:no-underline max-w-none"
        >
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            These terms govern your use of tam.buzz and the services of Tam
            Philosophical Counseling, operated by tambuzztam LLC.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4 text-amber-400">
            Cancellation and rescheduling
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            Sessions may be rescheduled or cancelled with at least 24 hours
            notice. Cancellations with at least 24 hours notice will receive a
            full refund. Sessions cancelled with less than 24 hours notice and
            no-shows are not eligible for a refund.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4 text-amber-400">
            No warranty
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            Services are provided as-is. tambuzztam LLC makes no guarantees
            about particular outcomes. Philosophical counseling is an inquiry
            into what you already know — the work depends on the engagement of
            both parties.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4 text-amber-400">
            Limitation of liability
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            To the fullest extent permitted by law, tambuzztam LLC shall not be
            liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages
            arising from your participation in philosophical counseling
            services.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4 text-amber-400">
            Governing law
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            These terms are governed by the laws of the State of Delaware.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4 text-amber-400">
            Changes to these terms
          </h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            We may update these terms from time to time. Changes will be posted
            here with an updated effective date.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4 text-amber-400">Contact</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            Questions? Reach us at <a
              href="mailto:info@tam.buzz"
              class="text-amber-400 hover:text-amber-300 no-underline"
              >info@tam.buzz</a
            >.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-white/10">
          <a
            href="/#cta"
            class="inline-flex items-center text-amber-400 hover:text-amber-300 no-underline transition-colors"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5 mr-2"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path>
            </svg>
            Back to Tam
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style is:global>
  html {
    scroll-snap-type: none;
  }
</style>
